CREDITS: https://pentestmonkey.net/cheat-sheet/sql-injection/mysql-sql-injection-cheat-sheet

Basic commands to test, at first:

Version:	SELECT @@version
Current User: 	SELECT user();
				SELECT system_user();
Current Database: 	SELECT database()
				
